Azure Portal:   https://portal.azure.com/#home
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Subscription vs Account:

Subscription is a logical container which contains the various resources you provision in the cloud such as VMs, DBs, Networks, etc.
Subscription can be attached to a lot of accounts. 

Account is an identity with access to resources in the subscription i.e. You. 
Account can be attached to a lot of subscriptions.
